data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: U.S. Marines with 1st Battalion, 5th Marine Regiment, 1st Marine Division, participate in the Aisne-Marne Memorial Day ceremony at the Aisne-Marne American Cemetery near Belleau, France, May 26, 2019. May 26, 2019. The ceremony commemorated the 101st anniversary of the Battle of Belleau Wood, which marked the first occasion in World War I for U.S. forces to operate on a large scale against the German Army. (U.S. Marine Corps photo by Miguel A. Rosales)
